# User Security Monitor

## Overview

User Security Monitor is a Python-based security monitoring tool that analyses login activity and identifies potentially suspicious behaviour.

The program checks:

- Blocked IP addresses
- Failed login attempts
- Suspicious login activity

This project simulates basic security monitoring tasks commonly performed by SOC analysts and cloud security engineers.

---

## Features

✅ User login monitoring

✅ Blocked IP detection

✅ Failed login analysis

✅ Suspicious activity alerts

✅ Security report generation

---

## Technologies Used

- Python 3
- Ubuntu Linux
- Nano Editor

